Matrix<org.molgenis.pheno.ObservedValue>
public class ObservedValueMatrix
extends MemoryMatrix<org.molgenis.pheno.ObservedValue>

Naive implementation of a datbase backed matrix that will base its view (order) on what features and targets there are set to be selected. No sorting, filtering or paging are part of this. Also duplicate observations of the same target,feature pair are not supported.
